headline: Will AI-Driven Expansion and New Partnerships Reshape GoDaddy's (GDDY) Growth Story?
summary: Earlier this month, GoDaddy announced the expansion of its AI-powered Digital Ads feature to nine new international markets, while media figures Laura Brown and Kristina O'Neill teamed up with GoDaddy to support entrepreneurs through career transitions by promoting new tools and exclusive offers for U.S. customers. This combination of AI-driven product expansion and high-profile partnerships highlights GoDaddy's ongoing efforts to make digital marketing and business setup more accessible to...
